{"id": "1280765423180054558", "channel_id": "1280765423180054558", "type": 0, "author_id": "501758744175181825", "author_name": "inukami2266", "author_bot": false, "content": "幻夢深潛的代理憑證掃蕩卷\n花錢買了季票才發現這玩意解不掉季票的任務次數..?\n也解不掉 每周試煉的 (1/5) ??\n可是這模式真的太久又卡一個死亡抵抗太難玩了\n有考慮買月卡玩家直接每天給一張卷之類的嗎?\n另外各種關卡的  \"重現\" 鈕可以改成直接完成每日的 使用 50張卡 每日試訓 任務嗎?\n\n代理憑證 = 每日試訓直接完成，但完成不了季票跟每周試練\n重現 = 花了體力掃蕩但你還是要另外找關卡丟 50 張卡", "timestamp": "2024-09-04T05:44:32.357000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1280765424019177472", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3285962, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1280765423180054558/1280765424019177472/image.png?ex=69cc0800&is=69cab680&hm=1555de611d751e651152e29853341f7f24e7ed5039e1fec57960b472a53480dd&"}, {"id": "1280765424870363157", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2451955, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1280765423180054558/1280765424870363157/image.png?ex=69cc0800&is=69cab680&hm=dd84132acbc84211d4a0401c4c7cfa5e064826b19d066f63a762c1575a1d8a46&"}, {"id": "1280765425440915500", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1032509, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1280765423180054558/1280765425440915500/image.png?ex=69cc0800&is=69cab680&hm=f44bbb8959261bf256c5192afc4f900a06793651f5dee30180c46103a6c31dac&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1280765423180054558", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "幻夢深潛的掃蕩卷", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
